{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Shopify Page / Theme Customization Prompt — AdHouse.in USP Sections
    
    Create a fully customizable USP (Why Choose Us) section for the AdHouse.in Shopify store. This section should be added to the About Us page or usable as a standalone homepage section. All settings must be editable from the Shopify Theme Editor with separate controls for mobile and desktop where specified.
    
    SECTION 1 — Real Photos vs AI Images Comparison
    Purpose: Build trust by showing customers that our product images are real, not AI-generated.
    Layout:
    
    Two-column side-by-side layout on desktop
    Stacked single column on mobile
    Left card labeled "AI Generated Image" with a red or pink subtle badge
    Right card labeled "Our Actual Product Photo" with a green badge
    A short line of text below each image explaining the difference
    Optional divider line or VS badge between the two columns
    
    Customizable settings in Theme Editor:
    
    Section heading text (default: "What You See Is What You Get")
    Subheading text (default: "Unlike others, we never use AI-generated images. Every photo is our actual product.")
    Left image upload (AI example photo)
    Right image upload (actual product photo)
    Left card badge text & badge color
    Right card badge text & badge color
    Caption text below each image
    Desktop font size for heading — range 24px to 48px
    Mobile font size for heading — range 18px to 32px
    Desktop caption font size — range 12px to 16px
    Mobile caption font size — range 11px to 14px
    Section background color
    Card background color
    Text color
    Toggle to show/hide the VS badge in the center
    Toggle to show/hide this entire section
    
    
    SECTION 2 — Honest Discounts, No Fake Pricing
    Purpose: Reassure customers that our discounts are genuine — we never inflate MRP to fake a sale.
    Layout:
    
    Full-width section with a bold headline
    Two comparison cards side by side on desktop, stacked on mobile
    Card 1 titled "How others do it" — showing inflated price → fake 50% off
    Card 2 titled "How AdHouse does it" — showing fair original price → real honest discount
    A short trust statement below both cards
    
    Customizable settings in Theme Editor:
    
    Section heading text (default: "No Drama. No Fake Discounts.")
    Subheading (default: "The price you see is honest. Always.")
    Card 1 title, description text, and accent color (default: soft red)
    Card 2 title, description text, and accent color (default: soft green)
    Trust statement text below cards
    Desktop heading font size — range 24px to 48px
    Mobile heading font size — range 18px to 32px
    Desktop card body font size — range 13px to 16px
    Mobile card body font size — range 12px to 15px
    Section background color
    Card background color
    Toggle to show/hide the comparison cards
    Toggle to show/hide this entire section
    
    
    SECTION 3 — Top-Notch Quality & Design
    Purpose: Highlight that every piece is handpicked, premium quality, and designed with care.
    Layout:
    
    Centered headline and subheading
    Icon + text grid below — 3 columns on desktop, 2 columns on mobile, 1 column on very small screens
    Each grid item has an icon (uploadable or emoji), a bold label, and a short description
    Optional product lifestyle image on the side or above the grid
    
    Default grid items (all editable):
    
    Handpicked Designs — "Every piece is personally curated, not bulk-sourced"
    Premium Finish — "Smooth edges, rich plating, flawless look"
    Occasion Ready — "From festivals to everyday wear"
    Attention to Detail — "Crafted to look expensive, priced to be accessible"
    
    Customizable settings in Theme Editor:
    
    Section heading and subheading text
    Number of grid columns on desktop (2, 3, or 4)
    Number of grid columns on mobile (1 or 2)
    Up to 6 grid items — each with icon upload, label text, description text, toggle to show/hide
    Desktop heading font size — range 24px to 44px
    Mobile heading font size — range 18px to 30px
    Desktop grid label font size — range 14px to 18px
    Mobile grid label font size — range 13px to 16px
    Desktop grid description font size — range 12px to 15px
    Mobile grid description font size — range 11px to 14px
    Icon size on desktop (range 32px to 64px)
    Icon size on mobile (range 24px to 48px)
    Section background color
    Icon accent color
    Label text color
    Description text color
    Toggle to show/hide this entire section
    
    
    SECTION 4 — Anti-Tarnish Tested
    Purpose: Show that AdHouse jewellery is physically tested for durability, tarnish resistance, and skin safety.
    Layout:
    
    Left side: bold headline, subheading, and a short paragraph
    Right side: a checklist of tested properties with checkmark icons
    On mobile: stacked, headline first then checklist
    Optional badge or seal image (e.g., "Lab Tested" or "Quality Assured")
    
    Default checklist items (all editable):
    
    Anti-tarnish tested
    Sweat and water resistant
    Long-lasting gold/silver plating
    Skin-safe and nickel-free
    Stress-tested for clasps and settings
    
    Customizable settings in Theme Editor:
    
    Section heading text (default: "Built to Last. Tested to Prove It.")
    Subheading and paragraph text
    Up to 8 checklist items — each with text and toggle to show/hide
    Ch
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-anti-tarnish-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.section_bg_color }};
  }

  .ai-anti-tarnish-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-anti-tarnish-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .ai-anti-tarnish-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding-right: 20px;
  }

  .ai-anti-tarnish-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.desktop_heading_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: {{ block.settings.heading_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.heading_font.fallback_families }};
  }

  .ai-anti-tarnish-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .ai-anti-tarnish-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.desktop_paragraph_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    opacity: 0.85;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 24px;
  }

  .ai-anti-tarnish-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .ai-anti-tarnish-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} img {
    max-width: 120px;
    height: auto;
  }

  .ai-anti-tarnish-checklist-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.checklist_bg_color }};
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .ai-anti-tarnish-checklist-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 24px;
  }

  .ai-anti-tarnish-checklist-items-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .ai-anti-tarnish-checklist-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.desktop_checklist_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-anti-tarnish-checkmark-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.checkmark_color }};
    color: #ffffff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-anti-tarnish-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.mobile_heading_size }}px;
    }

    .ai-anti-tarnish-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.mobile_paragraph_size }}px;
    }

    .ai-anti-tarnish-checklist-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.mobile_checklist_size }}px;
    }

    .ai-anti-tarnish-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .ai-anti-tarnish-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding-right: 0;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

{% if block.settings.show_section %}
  <ai-anti-tarnish-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-anti-tarnish-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
    <div class="ai-anti-tarnish-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-anti-tarnish-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <div class="ai-anti-tarnish-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
            <h2 class="ai-anti-tarnish-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
          {% endif %}
          {% if block.settings.subheading != blank %}
            <div class="ai-anti-tarnish-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.subheading }}</div>
          {% endif %}
          {% if block.settings.paragraph != blank %}
            <div class="ai-anti-tarnish-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.paragraph }}</div>
          {% endif %}
          {% if block.settings.badge_image %}
            <div class="ai-anti-tarnish-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <img
                src="{{ block.settings.badge_image | image_url: width: 240 }}"
                alt="{{ block.settings.badge_image.alt | escape }}"
                loading="lazy"
              >
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="ai-anti-tarnish-checklist-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.checklist_title != blank %}
            <h3 class="ai-anti-tarnish-checklist-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.checklist_title }}</h3>
          {% endif %}
          <div class="ai-anti-tarnish-checklist-items-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% for i in (1..8) %}
              {% liquid
                assign show_key = 'item_' | append: i | append: '_show'
                assign text_key = 'item_' | append: i | append: '_text'

                assign show_item = block.settings[show_key]
                assign item_text = block.settings[text_key]
              %}

              {% if show_item and item_text != blank %}
                <div class="ai-anti-tarnish-checklist-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <div class="ai-anti-tarnish-checkmark-{{ ai_gen_id }}">✓</div>
                  <span>{{ item_text }}</span>
                </div>
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </ai-anti-tarnish-{{ ai_gen_id }}>
{% endif %}

